{"tid":1849554,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟工人姨姨啲口罩去左邊","createTime":"2020-01-29T06:20:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-13T10:10:18.000Z","uid":117947,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"af73da9bcee6984fbda9fa9a9f9ad08bb3a62268","tid":1849554,"uid":117947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T06:20:46.000Z","msg":"話說之前我見到個工人EE唔戴口罩<br />\n咁我就叫佢帶返口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/41.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知佢一攞就攞咗10幾個收埋左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（我之後先知）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好，都算啦<br />\n有需要始終係要戴嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日撞到佢出門口<br />\n點知佢戴住個布口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n於是我叫佢戴番啲外科口罩😷<br />\n布口罩無用架，防唔到菌，只可以保暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n於是佢又攞左10個8個口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跟住我就同屋企人講番呢件事<br />\n點知屋企人話琴日已經俾左幾個口罩佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實佢啲口罩去左邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n會唔會拎左去賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c23a7bea94ad9888da45c5206da198fc34c22d51","tid":1849554,"uid":73241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T06:21:06.000Z","msg":"奶清<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28db408084f5bbd651b72805c57b53a90e1dbe61","tid":1849554,"uid":103759,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T06:21:48.000Z","msg":"想知口罩黑市價幾多"},{"pid":"02970324a3efbd1ca667534e4a5a32467c528ea3","tid":1849554,"uid":